## 2. Igniter.js Client Integration Protocol

**âš ï¸ IMPORTANT NOTE:** All examples in this section have been corrected based on the actual implementation found in the project codebase. The Igniter.js client has hooks available:

- **Queries**: `api.endpoint.useQuery()` returns `{ data: { data: T }, isLoading, error }`
